      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. load prev report + history\n2. build system prompt\n3. create_mcp_server(tools=...)\n4. ClaudeAgentOptions(\n     max_turns=30,\n     bypassPermissions=True)\n5. async for msg in query(...):\n     handle blocks\n6. post_stage_hook()\n7. publish_artifacts()\n8. update session.state",
